criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients scheduled for lumbar fusion surgery on account of vertebral fractures or
             degenerative spondylolisthesis.

          -  Patients consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Opioid tolerance;

          -  Documented sleep apnoea or home oxygen therapy;

          -  History of alcohol or drug abuse;

          -  Patients with an allergy or hypersensitivity to opioids.
